  "detailed_description": "Symmetry Lines is simple puzzle game with symmetry and lines.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe rule of this game is :<br />\r\n- just move the circle and position it in correct square.<br />\r\n- but you can't move circles directly.<br />\r\n- circles will move symmetrical to a line,<br />\r\n- and you will manipulate the line.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis game consists of 36 puzzles, and the level of difficulty increases gradually.<br />\r\nthere are 12 Steam achievements.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHave fun with this game!",
  "about_the_game": "Symmetry Lines is simple puzzle game with symmetry and lines.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe rule of this game is :<br />\r\n- just move the circle and position it in correct square.<br />\r\n- but you can't move circles directly.<br />\r\n- circles will move symmetrical to a line,<br />\r\n- and you will manipulate the line.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis game consists of 36 puzzles, and the level of difficulty increases gradually.<br />\r\nthere are 12 Steam achievements.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHave fun with this game!",
